  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: 1.3.5\nOS & Version: Linux\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nThe geth should exit when `if(true){exit}` is typed in geth console\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nIt is not exiting and throws `ReferenceError: 'exit' is not defined`\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n1. Open geth console\n2. type in `if(true){exit}`\n",
